  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animal
    This class is an abstract class that represents all animals.
    Appointment
    Represents an appointment and has fields for the date, time, which pet, the owner, and if it is completed or not.
    Bird
    This class represents a Bird which can be of 5 types of bird
    Dog
    This class represents a dog which can be of 5 types of dog
    Engine
    The engine is used purely to add appointments, animals, and owners to an array list that can be accessed by the UserInput class to print out certain information.
    Fish
    This class represents a fish which can be of 5 types of fish
    Main
    Main class creates an Engine and a UserInterface
    MedicalRecord
    This class represents a medical record.
    Owner
    Represents the owner which has fields for their name, address, phone number, and list of all their pets.
    Save
    Used to save and load
    UserInterface
    Takes input from the user and prints our information.
